CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 3, 1970, pg. 17 reads: "An Attractive Trio - Three of the attractive young ladies who modeled at the Harriet Tubman Guild's recent "Winter Fantasy," are shown above. Members of Letha Hunt's Mona Lisas are from left to right :Marian Henderson, Diane Franklin and Sondria Pettigrew. - Harris photos."
TitMainTitle: Mona Lisa members, from left: Marian Henderson, Diane (Dalton) Franklin, and Sondria Pettigrew, posing in formal interior with triangular patterned carpeting for Harriet Tubman Guild "Winter Fantasy" fashion show
